zig-out/
.zig-cache/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.o
*.swp
.browdie/
tweet.md
.benchmarks/
# QuickJS-NG sources auto-fetched by `zig build` into a content-addressed
# subdir under zig-pkg/. The vendored `vendor/curl-impersonate/` IS tracked,
# but anything starting with `N-V-__` or matching the zig pkg-hash format
# is build cache. zig-pkg/ as a whole is not tracked except for vendor/.
zig-pkg/N-V-__*/
benchmarks/results/*
!benchmarks/results/README.md
!benchmarks/results/20260327-111742-https_vercel.com/
!benchmarks/results/20260327-111742-https_vercel.com/**
!benchmarks/results/20260327-111817-https_www.google.com_travel_flights_q=Flights%20to%20TPE%20from%/
!benchmarks/results/20260327-111817-https_www.google.com_travel_flights_q=Flights%20to%20TPE%20from%/**
